query:
SELECT uc.user_id, uc.username, up.perfil_ativo, up.is_medico, up.is_paciente 
FROM user_credentials uc 
LEFT JOIN user_profiles up ON uc.user_id = up.user_id 
WHERE uc.username = 'leticia.uzeika';
